name: Drink Master Says
description:
DrinkMaster Says is the ultimate party in a pack. The game is an exciting mix of rules and challenges loaded with non-stop action. Once you start playing you may never want to stop! 

The object of the game is to be the first player to get rid of all your cards. Along the way, you might have to drink with no hands, balance stuff on your head, or be a part of a burping competition, just to name a few. 

So gather your friends, pop open your favorite beverage and deal out the cards – Find out who among you can truly be called DrinkMaster!

name: Yankey Hankey
description:
Duck Did Design Inc. has put together one hilarious novelty item with the brand new Yankey Hankey Gift Set! 

The gift set includes a funny Yankey Hankey TM screen-printed cloth and an outrageous, side splitting, 48-page book filled with everything you need to know about playing with your Mister Happy. It is the perfect joke gift to bust your friends’ chops, to teenagers heading off to college and to men entering into the world of married life.

name: Naughty Bachelorette
description:
All girls have the right to a wild bachelorette party. Why not make it happen with The Naughty Bachelorette Party Tickets? 

Each package contains everything you’ll need to loosen things up and make this an unforgettable last night of freedom for the bride-to-be. The tickets have a list of crimes and fines. You cite a person on a playful infraction, and you choose how they are to repay their debt to society: naughty or nice, mild or wild!

Each set includes:

3 customizable badges
1 Ticket Tablet
1 Pencil
